Class Session

  • java.lang.Object
    • Session

  • public class Session
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a ticketmachine session The "session" increases user-machine interaction efficiency, by reducing the number of user actions required. This is achieved by: - Making a TicketMachine object automatically - Having a method which calls multiple other required methods
